</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[189,1399,447,508]" pageId="3" pageNumber="100">
The name refers to the name given by the Rapa Nui people to the 
<typeStatus box="[944,995,448,474]" pageId="3" pageNumber="100">type</typeStatus>
locality, 'Motu Motiro Hiva'; noun in apposition.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
